      <title>法国加大对企业和富人的“巨额”债务打击力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/french-economy-latest-france-taxes-companies-wealthy-to-tackle-debt-pile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府公布了明年的预算，旨在投入 606 亿欧元（662 亿美元）来弥补公共财政的不足，重建投资者信心，尽管法国政府有可能被敌对的议会驱逐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/french-economy-latest-france-taxes-companies-wealthy-to-tackle-debt-pile</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国任命前 Darktrace 首席执行官 Gustafsson 为新任投资部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uk-names-former-darktrace-ceo-gustafsson-new-investment-minister-m23lmrge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 任命前 Darktrace 首席执行官 Poppy Gustafsson 为英国新任投资部长，在伦敦举行的重要商业峰会前几天，她终于上任了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uk-names-former-darktrace-ceo-gustafsson-new-investment-minister-m23lmrge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 17:55:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢旺达迅速应对，马尔堡疫情几乎消除全球风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/marburg-s-global-risk-of-spread-almost-eliminated-by-rwanda-s-quick-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于卢旺达这个东非国家采取了快速且高度协调的应对措施，控制住了该国首次出现的马尔堡病毒疫情，因此，这种病毒从卢旺达向国际蔓延的风险几乎为零。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/marburg-s-global-risk-of-spread-almost-eliminated-by-rwanda-s-quick-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 17:44:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提议将汽车贷款利息完全免税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/trump-to-propose-making-car-loan-interest-fully-tax-deductible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将于周四在摇摆州密歇根州发表经济讲话，承诺将汽车贷款利息完全免税，以帮助促进美国汽车业的发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/trump-to-propose-making-car-loan-interest-fully-tax-deductible</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 17:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国成立咨询小组助力实现2030年清洁能源目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uk-forms-advisory-panel-to-help-deliver-2030-clean-power-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国召集了八名来自工业界和学术界的专家，以帮助该国实现到本世纪末实现电网脱碳的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uk-forms-advisory-panel-to-help-deliver-2030-clean-power-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 17:18:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列安全内阁将就伊朗问题举行会议，拜登呼吁保持克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/israel-security-cabinet-to-meet-on-iran-as-biden-urges-restraint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列安全内阁准备于周四晚间开会讨论如何对伊朗上周的导弹袭击进行报复，但美国影响该决定的努力仍存在疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/israel-security-cabinet-to-meet-on-iran-as-biden-urges-restraint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:33:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高利率令借款人举步维艰，加拿大收入差距创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/income-gap-is-widest-on-record-in-canada-as-high-rates-pinch-borrowers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大的收入不平等现象已达到本世纪最大，高利率增加了低收入家庭的债务负担，同时提高了高收入人群的投资收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/income-gap-is-widest-on-record-in-canada-as-high-rates-pinch-borrowers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:17:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥准备任命 Sheinbaum 的盟友 Alarcón 为世界银行特使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/mexico-poised-to-name-sheinbaum-ally-alarcon-as-world-bank-envoy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆将任命数十年的盟友和知己为墨西哥驻世界银行最高代表，新上任的领导人将致力于减少贫困和促进发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/mexico-poised-to-name-sheinbaum-ally-alarcon-as-world-bank-envoy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:05:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称军队缺乏装备，计划于 11 月举行峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/zelenskiy-says-forces-lack-equipment-aims-for-november-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，他的军队正面临军事装备短缺的问题，他强调将于下个月举行第二次峰会，以推动结束俄罗斯战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/zelenskiy-says-forces-lack-equipment-aims-for-november-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:03:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
