      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/israeli-army-deliberately-killed-doctors-in-gaza-un-panel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国小组称，以色列齐心协力摧毁加沙的医疗系统，包括故意杀害战区的医务人员。]]></description>
